The suspect appeared in the Thembalethu Magistrate s Court on Monday.According to police spokesman Captain Dumile Gwavu the bag contained 298 mandrax tablets and one gram of tik.Police stopped the vehicle with two men in it after receiving information about a maroon VW Jetta transporting drugs from George. The vehicle was seen by the police in Thembalethu. The police followed the vehicle and stopped it on the N2 highway Gwavu said.